Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:53.87,Default1,,0,0,0,,這… 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:56.29,Default1,,0,0,0,,與以往不一樣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:58.37,Default1,,0,0,0,,妳們冷靜聽我解釋
