Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:32.43,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Drive ignition{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}魔導驅動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.25,0:23:20.69,Default1,,0,0,0,,她們的魔導器…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.15,0:23:22.42,Default1,,0,0,0,,那莫非是…！？
